    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2648112511" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2648112511" />
    <a title="Apurva Nagpal" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/74772284-apurva-nagpal"><img alt="Apurva Nagpal" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1512822277p2/74772284.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2648112511?book_show_action=true">Jan 03, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Apurva Nagpal" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Apurva Nagpal" href="/user/show/74772284-apurva-nagpal">Apurva Nagpal</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/74772284-apurva-nagpal?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2648112511" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4012425299383109182">“Vision without action is merely a dream; action without vision is merely passing time; but vision and action together can change the world.”<br/><br/>Wise and Otherwise by Sudha Murty is a collection of 50 real life experiences of the author, told in the form of short stories.<br/>Each story tells us about various incidents or her confrontation with some bitter truths of life, some with real eye opening situations and some really beautiful memories, each leaving us with a simple yet powerful message.<br/>I couldn&apos;</span>
  <span id="freeText4012425299383109182" style="display:none">“Vision without action is merely a dream; action without vision is merely passing time; but vision and action together can change the world.”<br /><br />Wise and Otherwise by Sudha Murty is a collection of 50 real life experiences of the author, told in the form of short stories.<br />Each story tells us about various incidents or her confrontation with some bitter truths of life, some with real eye opening situations and some really beautiful memories, each leaving us with a simple yet powerful message.<br />I couldn't stop reading this chapter after chapter and her shared experiences have touched my heart.<br /><br />Some stories and incidents were life changing for the author and to read them is indeed so inspiring and this is truly A Salute to life.<br />I give this one ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️/5 and highly recommend it if you’re looking for a light and quick read.</span>
  <a data-text-id="4012425299383109182" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


